{"tid":816223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天氣消息","createTime":"2018-09-12T15:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T15:39:35.000Z","uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4d8aeb5c683b6bb159bebe5ee2211b093cf55e4","tid":816223,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:03:13.000Z","msg":"今日天氣不穩，暴雨襲港，今年首個黑色暴雨警告信號一度生效。天文台今早6時40分先發出黃色暴雨警告，至上午9時15分改發紅色暴雨警告信號，為今年首個紅雨警告。隨後另一個雨帶從珠江口移近香港，天文台於上午11時30分改發今年首個黑色暴雨警告信號，生效1小時後，於中午12時30分改發黃雨警告，隨後至下午3時取消所有暴雨警告。<br />\n<br />\n天文台表示，今早廣泛地區錄得超過70毫米雨量，而葵青及深水埗更超過300毫米。雷暴警告、新界北部水浸特別報告及山泥傾瀉警告亦先後生效。<br />\n<br />\n受暴雨影響，教育局宣布，所有下午校停課。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170524/bkn-20170524065021727-0524_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170524%2Fbkn-20170524065021727-0524_00822_001.html&d=4bHX7xMxKbaLYX4XVtwEP6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=fa285738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170524/bkn-20170524065021727-0524_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"969c2dc0b2b6d15474b971fc3b2a9c666ee59367","tid":816223,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:17:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97b1774d3cf8295359a5c46bf2f999fbea10e92e","tid":816223,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bbd4ccb3ae0924092d752e6235845d4dd9da9c","tid":816223,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}